---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import benchPlaneImage from "../assets/images/bench-plane-frog_adobe_express.svg";
import complianceImage from "../assets/images/compliance.jpeg";
import sustainabilityImage from "../assets/images/sustainability_logo.svg";
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="w-full container mx-auto px-8 py-12">
    <div class="flex justify-left">
      <nav class="text-sm sm:text-base pb-6">
        <ol class="list-none p-0 inline-flex space-x-2">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              onclick="window.location.href='/';"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              height="1em"
              viewBox="0 0 576 512"
              class="cursor-pointer hover:fill-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300 mr-2"
              fill="#4b5563"
              ><!--! Font Awesome Free 6.4.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. -->
              <path
                d="M575.8 255.5c0 18-15 32.1-32 32.1h-32l.7 160.2c0 2.7-.2 5.4-.5 8.1V472c0 22.1-17.9 40-40 40H456c-1.1 0-2.2 0-3.3-.1c-1.4 .1-2.8 .1-4.2 .1H416 392c-22.1 0-40-17.9-40-40V448 384c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32H256c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32v64 24c0 22.1-17.9 40-40 40H160 128.1c-1.5 0-3-.1-4.5-.2c-1.2 .1-2.4 .2-3.6 .2H104c-22.1 0-40-17.9-40-40V360c0-.9 0-1.9 .1-2.8V287.6H32c-18 0-32-14-32-32.1c0-9 3-17 10-24L266.4 8c7-7 15-8 22-8s15 2 21 7L564.8 231.5c8 7 12 15 11 24z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
          </li>

          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="text-yellow-600 font-semibold">About</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight pb-4">About</h1>

    <h4 class="text-xl font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      Crafting Exceptional Spaces with Heart and Expertise
    </h4>
    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      Coulsy Joinery is a family-owned carpentry and joinery business, founded
      and operated by Robert, a seasoned professional joiner with a passion for
      creating beautiful, functional spaces. With over three decades of
      experience in carpentry and joinery, Robert brings a wealth of knowledge
      and craftsmanship to every project.
    </p>
    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      A premier provider of carpentry and joinery services, including bespoke
      garden offices and rooms. Robert's later journey began with a simple idea:
      to help people make the most of their outdoor spaces. Today, he continue
      to innovate and expand, guided by our core values of quality,
      sustainability, and customer satisfaction.
    </p>
    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      Working alongside him is his wife, whose dedication and skills are
      integral to the success of the business. Together, they lead a small,
      skilled team that shares their commitment to quality and customer
      satisfaction. This close-knit team ensures that every project receives the
      personal attention it deserves, resulting in bespoke solutions tailored to
      each clientâ€™s needs.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-light mb-4 mt-4">
      Delivering to your needs and requiremnents
    </h2>
    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      At Coulsy Joinery, we understand the need for rules and regulations. They
      are there for you, us and others, so that standards can be maintained,
      guidance followed and where possible go that extra mile in our efforts to
      make a sustainable company and protect our natural resources.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div
        class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 dark:shadow-none dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-50 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <Image
            src={benchPlaneImage}
            alt="woodworking bench plane"
            loading="eager"
            width="1000"
            height="667"
            class="h-64 w-full object-cover object-top transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
          <div class="mt-6 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
              Fully Qualified
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Our team are highly qualified to meet the demands of your
              project...
            </p>
            <a class="inline-block" href="/about/qualifications">
              <span class="text-info dark:text-blue-300">Read more</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 dark:shadow-none dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-50 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <Image
            src={complianceImage}
            alt="compliance"
            loading="eager"
            width="1000"
            height="667"
            class="h-64 w-full object-cover object-top transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
          <div class="mt-6 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
              Highly Compliant
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              We adhere to the highest standards of compliance and ethics...
            </p>
            <a class="inline-block" href="/about/compliance">
              <span class="text-info dark:text-blue-300">Read more</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 dark:shadow-none dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-50 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <Image
            src={sustainabilityImage}
            alt="sustainability"
            loading="eager"
            width="1000"
            height="667"
            class="h-64 w-full object-cover object-top transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
          <div class="mt-6 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
              Sustainability
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Making a difference...
            </p>
            <a class="inline-block" href="/about/sustainability">
              <span class="text-info dark:text-blue-300">Read more</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
